The Postmaster of Mafdet has received an expedition commission for a complete navigation survey of the ancient pyramid complex. The pyramid is a significant structure in the desert region, and its internal layout has not been comprehensively documented in the harbor authority's reference files. Chart every accessible chamber, passage, and approach route within the pyramid and return with a full survey record.
Your pyramid survey has been filed with Mafdet's harbor authority expedition archive. The completed navigation record has replaced the incomplete documentation previously held, and expedition crews operating in the pyramid will now have access to a reliable full survey.
